reviewText: Loved the PBS show that you cannot find elsewhere our lOcal channel took it off he air.  Great family viewing. Good lessons. Multiple shows on one DVD.

I got this thinking it was the first dvd, but its the second!
its still packed with 5 of the saddle club eppisodes! that i love! <3
great for a saddle club lover from series 1 and 2 like me or season 3!!! :)
young and old will love the saddle club!
